How to prepare a release

- bootinstall, test, commit
- in build.xml, update the property stable.version
- commit, tag the release with
	cvs -d $GFORGE rtag -R tom-2_4rc1 jtom
- create distfiles: ./build.sh dist.all
                    ./build.sh source.distribution
- upload files to gforge

- add news entry in jtom-doc/www/{index.php,news.php} 

- update tom manual version (template.hva, tom.sty)
- build manual
- upload manual
